#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIS.rst:53
#: eb57ad63e31c4324bf8cae46dbf0bd84
msgid ""
"Node transitions follow two rules: 1) if a :math:`S` state node has "
":math:`I` state neighbors, each :math:`I` state neighbor transmits the "
"infection to the :math:`S` state node with probability :math:`\\beta`; 2)"
" the :math:`I` state node recovers and becomes susceptible again with "
"probability :math:`\\gamma`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIS.rst:57
#: fb9e8234afd643b685b29c1b5d12ad31
msgid "SIS model diagram"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIS.rst:62
#: 8326b1fb2ff7444fa78f77184f664afc
msgid ""
"Node states are represented by a Boolean indicator vector :math:`h \\in "
"\\{0,1\\}^N`, where :math:`h_i=1` denotes ``infected`` and :math:`h_i=0` "
"denotes ``susceptible``. The update of the system at step :math:`k` is "
"decomposed into three stages:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIS.rst:66
#: 576123d5f33e4dbb9af861e0031c9df6
msgid ""
"Each infected neighbor :math:`j` of node :math:`i` transmits a log-"
"probability contribution"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIS.rst:68
#: 72225ad1bdc24ca6b5a26b9984aa461d
msgid "m_{ji}^{(k)} = h_j^{(k-1)} \\cdot \\log(1-\\beta)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIS.rst:72
#: 0c762f4ff77949c194ac540fe69ecb15
msgid ""
"Node :math:`i` collects contributions from all neighbors :math:`N(i)` to "
"compute its infection probability"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIS.rst:74
#: 78a8969e298a43b59958be61b4834d29
msgid "m_i^{(k)} = 1 - \\exp\\!\\left( \\sum_{j \\in N(i)} m_{ji}^{(k)} \\right)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIS.rst:79
#: 6f5781cb2cc44decaa33bc1e44a20a32
msgid ""
"3) The indicator variable is updated with independent uniform random "
"variables :math:`U_i^{\\mathrm{inf}}, U_i^{\\mathrm{rec}} \\sim "
"\\mathrm{Uniform}(0,1)`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SIS.rst:82
#: 44fb059a391441f3ac4417581280578b
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"h_i^{(k)} &=\n"
"\\begin{cases}\n"
"   1, & \\text{if } h_i^{(k-1)}=0 \\land (U_i^{\\mathrm{inf}} < "
"m_i^{(k)}), \\\\[4pt]\n"
"   0, & \\text{if } h_i^{(k-1)}=1 \\land (U_i^{\\mathrm{rec}} < \\gamma),"
" \\\\[4pt]\n"
"   h_i^{(k-1)}, & \\text{otherwise}.\n"
"\\end{cases}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

